  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/7657f1409f3b2090c01e036adeb0610c046285ea/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/Program.cs#L98-L99\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/7657f1409f3b2090c01e036adeb0610c046285ea/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Api/Extensions/PluginLoader.cs#L38-L43\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/7657f1409f3b2090c01e036adeb0610c046285ea/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Api/Extensions/PluginLoader.cs#L56\r\n\r\nNowhere in the loading process for plugins does Nethermind actually read the `Init.PluginsDirectory` configuration option.  One challenge here is that currently the `PluginLoader` is run *before* configuration is read.  I'm not sure if this is required, or we could just move the PluginLoader` to after configuration read.",
